data.description: Welcome to this charming Plumas Lake home. This home boasts a spacious and well-designed layout with 4 BDRM + Loft & 3 baths providing ample space for your family's needs. The 1st floor has a comfortable and versatile BDRM & full bath. Also a living room, family room and dining room, allowing you to create cherished memories with loved ones. The property has recently undergone updates, including brand new LVP flooring throughout the downstairs area, a fresh coat of paint to infuse a sense of brightness, a newer HVAC system, and a newly landscaped front/back yard to enhance its curb appeal. Embrace the outdoor lifestyle with a backyard that includes a large patio, perfect for hosting gatherings and enjoying delightful BBQs with friends and family. The spacious side access accommodates a small boat or trailer, offering a great advantage for outdoor enthusiasts. This home enjoys the benefits of a wonderful community and proximity to amenities, schools and parks. No HOA and low Mello Roos. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a spacious beautifully updated home. Make this house your dream home and create a lifetime of cherished memories!
